	* libgnomevfs/gnome-vfs-init.c: (gnome_vfs_initialized):
	* libgnomevfs/gnome-vfs-init.h:

	Add gnome_vfs_initialized so you can check if gnome-vfs has been
	initialized already, without it whining.
	
