	Added gnome_vfs_uri_get_path function.

	(gnome_vfs_uri_get_basename):
	Added FIXME bug id 1472.

	* modules/ftp-method.h:
	* modules/ftp-method.c: (FTP_DEBUG), (read_response_line),
	(do_path_command), (do_path_command_completely),
